CiviSearch Plugin

Author:  Lighthouse Consulting and Design
Url:     http://www.lcdservices.biz
Created: August, 2011

Joomla search plugin to provide access to CiviCRM resources through the Joomla search tools. The plugin will be compatible with Joomla 1.5 and 1.6+. It currently provides for searching of CiviCRM events, using the event title, summary, and description fields, and returning a link to the event information page.

CHANGELOG:
2011-08-18 :: v1.0 :: initial release with J1.5, J1.6+ compatibility
2011-08-23 :: v1.1 :: add option to set menuitem when link is built
